{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-tsx","path":"/travel/2020/06/27/蛇口仅剩的一家魅族线下体验店.html","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"a32348bd-a7e7-5c50-af59-66e005923e3f","excerpt":"蛇口仅剩的一家魅族线下体验店 在育才中学附近有一个蛇口仅存的一家魅族线下体验店。  店面有点寒酸，起码对比于万象天地的小米和华为的气派，只能说寒酸。  店面一侧摆着魅族 17 和魅族 16，这回主要看白色，旁边的黑色就没去看。  不得不说有点喜欢，之前就看上了小米 Mix2s…","html":"<h1>蛇口仅剩的一家魅族线下体验店</h1>\n<p>在育才中学附近有一个蛇口仅存的一家魅族线下体验店。</p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 400px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/8369f6ed158cf6527705774a9d3295ba/066f9/m2.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 50%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/8369f6ed158cf6527705774a9d3295ba/cbe2e/m2.webp 148w,\n/static/8369f6ed158cf6527705774a9d3295ba/3084c/m2.webp 295w,\n/static/8369f6ed158cf6527705774a9d3295ba/7f61c/m2.webp 400w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/8369f6ed158cf6527705774a9d3295ba/a80bd/m2.jpg 148w,\n/static/8369f6ed158cf6527705774a9d3295ba/1c91a/m2.jpg 295w,\n/static/8369f6ed158cf6527705774a9d3295ba/066f9/m2.jpg 400w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\"\n          type=\"image/jpeg\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/8369f6ed158cf6527705774a9d3295ba/066f9/m2.jpg\"\n          alt=\"魅族线下体验店\"\n          title=\"魅族线下体验店\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">魅族线下体验店</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p>店面有点寒酸，起码对比于万象天地的小米和华为的气派，只能说寒酸。</p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 400px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/9e21b0ccb072b2f82078dcf9304da23f/066f9/m3.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 51.35135135135135%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/9e21b0ccb072b2f82078dcf9304da23f/cbe2e/m3.webp 148w,\n/static/9e21b0ccb072b2f82078dcf9304da23f/3084c/m3.webp 295w,\n/static/9e21b0ccb072b2f82078dcf9304da23f/7f61c/m3.webp 400w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/9e21b0ccb072b2f82078dcf9304da23f/a80bd/m3.jpg 148w,\n/static/9e21b0ccb072b2f82078dcf9304da23f/1c91a/m3.jpg 295w,\n/static/9e21b0ccb072b2f82078dcf9304da23f/066f9/m3.jpg 400w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\"\n          type=\"image/jpeg\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/9e21b0ccb072b2f82078dcf9304da23f/066f9/m3.jpg\"\n          alt=\"华为线下体验店\"\n          title=\"华为线下体验店\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">华为线下体验店</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p>店面一侧摆着魅族 17 和魅族 16，这回主要看白色，旁边的黑色就没去看。</p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 400px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/cf42b0d5e3e12717497ad16a2c110044/066f9/m1.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 133.78378378378378%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/cf42b0d5e3e12717497ad16a2c110044/cbe2e/m1.webp 148w,\n/static/cf42b0d5e3e12717497ad16a2c110044/3084c/m1.webp 295w,\n/static/cf42b0d5e3e12717497ad16a2c110044/7f61c/m1.webp 400w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/cf42b0d5e3e12717497ad16a2c110044/a80bd/m1.jpg 148w,\n/static/cf42b0d5e3e12717497ad16a2c110044/1c91a/m1.jpg 295w,\n/static/cf42b0d5e3e12717497ad16a2c110044/066f9/m1.jpg 400w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\"\n          type=\"image/jpeg\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/cf42b0d5e3e12717497ad16a2c110044/066f9/m1.jpg\"\n          alt=\"白色的魅族17\"\n          title=\"白色的魅族17\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">白色的魅族17</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p>不得不说有点喜欢，之前就看上了小米 Mix2s 白色版，可是只能买到黑色的，挖孔屏的电量处理也很得我心意，重量嘛，虽然比我期望的魅族的重量要沉，但比我现在的手机轻。</p>\n<p>背面虽然看起来是磨砂，但摸起来有些胶质的感觉，可能和我的期望有点不同，到也谈不上失望或是惊喜。</p>\n<p>今年手机都上 5G 了，可我并不看好，除了电量损耗和手机质量的提升，5G 信号覆盖不全而且价格也不低…这种低性价比的东西若不是国家硬推，真是完全不能打，我搞不清楚为什么我要为它付费。</p>","frontmatter":{"category":"travel"},"fields":{"slug":"/travel/2020/06/27/蛇口仅剩的一家魅族线下体验店.html","date":"June 27, 2020","title":"蛇口仅剩的一家魅族线下体验店"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/travel/2020/06/27/蛇口仅剩的一家魅族线下体验店.html","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/plan/2020/06/24/海南旅行计划.html","title":"海南旅行计划"},"frontmatter":{"category":"plan"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/travel/2020/06/27/南山博物馆浮世绘展.html","title":"南山博物馆浮世绘展"},"frontmatter":{"category":"travel"}}}}}